## Struktur Final — IOT-Lanjutan (16 Pertemuan)

> **Edge AI (TinyML) DIHAPUS.** Sesi 9-10 lama (TinyML, Anomaly Detection) dihilangkan. Sesi-sesi setelahnya digeser maju, dan slot yang terbuka diisi dengan materi Home Assistant dan Computer Vision yang lebih mendalam.

| # | Topik | Asal / Perubahan |
|---|---|---|
| 1 | Inter-ESP32 UART | Sama (P1 lama) |
| 2 | Inter-ESP32 I2C Master/Slave | Sama (P2 lama) |
| 3 | ESP-NOW Point-to-Point | Sama (P3 lama) |
| 4 | ESP-NOW Gateway Multi-Node → MQTT Bridge | Sama (P4 lama) |
| 5 | HTTP GET — REST API Consumption | Sama (P5 lama) |
| 6 | HTTP POST — Kirim Data ke Server | Sama (P6 lama) |
| 7 | MQTT Part 1 — Arsitektur & Setup Broker Mosquitto | Sama (P7 lama) |
| 8 | MQTT Part 2 — ESP32 Publisher & Subscriber | Sama (P8 lama) |
| 9 | **Home Assistant Advanced & ESPHome Lanjutan** | **BARU** (slot P9 — ganti Edge AI) |
| 10 | **HA Automasi, Dashboard & Integrasi MQTT** | **BARU** (slot P10 — ganti Edge AI) |
| 11 | ESP32-CAM — Setup & MJPEG Streaming | Geser dari P11 lama |
| 12 | Computer Vision On-Device — Face Detection (ESP-WHO) | Geser dari P12 lama |
| 13 | Computer Vision — OpenCV Color Tracking + MQTT | Geser dari P13 lama |
| 14 | Computer Vision — YOLO + MediaPipe Gesture | Geser dari P14 lama |
| 15 | Arsitektur Sistem Terpadu & Persiapan Proyek | Sama (P15 lama) |
| 16 | Proyek Akhir — Presentasi | Sama (P16 lama) |

### Detail Materi Baru Home Assistant (IOT-Lanjutan)

**P9 — Home Assistant Advanced & ESPHome Lanjutan:**
- ESPHome custom sensor components (C++ lambda)
- ESPHome OTA + logging + fallback hotspot
- HA Add-ons: Mosquitto Broker, File Editor, Terminal
- ESPHome sebagai MQTT bridge (dual mode: native API + MQTT)
- Integrasi sensor IoT Lanjutan (ESP-NOW nodes) ke HA via ESPHome gateway

**P10 — HA Automasi, Dashboard & Integrasi MQTT:**
- HA Automations: trigger, condition, action — YAML dan UI
- HA Dashboard: Lovelace cards (gauge, graph, button, entity)
- HA + MQTT: ESP32 PubSubClient → HA MQTT integration (auto-discovery)
- HA Scenes & Scripts untuk kontrol multi-perangkat
- Notifikasi: HA → Telegram/Companion App

